<p>The Nation: How Georgia Indicted a Movement</p>
<p><a href="https://www.thenation.com/article/society/cop-city-indictment-atlanta/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferer">https://www.thenation.com/article/society/cop-city-indictment-atlanta/</a></p>
<p>Revolution: RICO Indictment Against Cop City Protesters:</p>
<p>An Ominous and Illegitimate Fascist Assault on Legitimate and Righteous Protest</p>
<p><a href="https://revcom.us/en/rico-indictment-against-cop-city-protesters-ominous-and-illegitimate-fascist-assault-legitimate-and">https://revcom.us/en/rico-indictment-against-cop-city-protesters-ominous-and-illegitimate-fascist-assault-legitimate-and</a></p>
