			<description><![CDATA[<p>Sam interviews Stephen Vladeck, law professor and author of the NY Times bestseller, <a href="https://www.hachettebookgroup.com/titles/stephen-vladeck/the-shadow-docket/9781541602632/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferer"><em>The Shadow Docket, How the Supreme Court Uses Stealth Rulings to Amass Power and Undermine the Republic</em></a>. Follow Steve on Twitter at <a href="https://twitter.com/steve_vladeck" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferer">@steve_vladeck</a> and sign up for his Substack here: <a href="https://stevevladeck.substack.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferer">stevevladeck.substack.com</a>.</p>
