			<title><![CDATA[Carrie Baker: Looming Decision That Could Ban Abortion Medication]]></title>
			<description><![CDATA[<p>Sam talks to Dr. Carrie Baker, Professor at Smith College and contributing editor of Ms. magazine about the lawsuit that could be decided in the coming days which would potentially eliminate access to medication induced abortions in the US. Follow <a href="https://msmagazine.com/author/carriebaker/">her work at Ms. magazine here</a> and follow her on Twitter at <a href="https://twitter.com/CarrieNBaker">@CarrieNBaker</a>.</p>
