<p><a href="https://riseup4abortionrights.org/fascist-judges-keep-your-hands-off-abortion-medication/">Fascist Judges: Keep Your Hands Off Abortion Medication!</a> (<a href="http://riseup4abortionrights.org/">RiseUp4AbortionRights.org</a>)</p>
<p>Mentioned in the episode:</p>
<h2>Episode 124: <a href="https://anchor.fm/refuse-fascism/episodes/Talking-Forced-Birth-in-Victorian-Times-and-Now-With-Kate-Manning-e1n313k">Talking Forced-Birth in Victorian Times and Now With Kate Manning</a></h2>
