			<title><![CDATA[The Aftermath of the Midterms]]></title>
			<description><![CDATA[<p>Sam Goldman chats with fellow RefuseFascism.org co-editors Coco Das and Paul Street about the aftermath of the 2022 midterms, Donald Trump declaring his 2024 candidacy and associated happenings this past week. Follow Coco on Twitter at <a href="https://twitter.com/coco_das">@Coco_Das</a> and subscribe to Paul on Substack at <a href="https://paulstreet.substack.com/">paulstreet.substack.com</a>. Read Paul's book <a href="https://www.routledge.com/This-Happened-Here-Amerikaners-Neoliberals-and-the-Trumping-of-America/Street/p/book/9781032150598"><em>This Happened Here: Amerikaners, Neoliberals, and the Trumping of America</em> </a>.</p>
<p><strong>Thursday, Dec. 1 </strong>From <a href="https://riseup4abortionrights.org/nov-25-dec-1/">RiseUp4AbortionRights.org</a>: Manifest in green and protest nationwide at &nbsp;courthouses around the country on Thursday December 1, the one-year &nbsp;anniversary of when the Supreme Court heard oral arguments in the case &nbsp;that overturned abortion rights. Through speeches, dramatic &nbsp;bloody die-ins, and in other ways, the protests should make clear that &nbsp;we cannot rely on the courts and have to rely on ourselves to rise up to &nbsp;win legal abortion on demand and without apology everywhere. Find or host a protest here: <a href="https://riseup4abortionrights.org/nov-25-dec-1/">https://riseup4abortionrights.org/nov-25-dec-1/</a></p>
<p>Refuse Fascism is more than a podcast! You can get involved at RefuseFascism.org. We're still on Twitter and other social platforms including the newest addition: <a href="https://mastodon.world/@refusefascism">mastodon.world/@refusefascism</a></p>
<p>It's getting cold now, and you may be thinking about holiday giving. Refuse Fascism beanies are extra warm and a great way to proudly declare where you stand this winter. Volunteers are standing by to ship one or five or 20 to you, <a href="https://refusefascism.bigcartel.com/product/refuse-fascism-beanie">so order here</a>!</p>
<p>Send &nbsp;your comments to samanthagoldman@refusefascism.org or <a href="https://twitter.com/SamBGoldman">@SamBGoldman</a>. Connect with the movement at <a href="https://refusefascism.org/">RefuseFascism.org</a> and support:</p>
