			<title><![CDATA[Post-Roe Reality Check & January 6 Hearing Update]]></title>
			<description><![CDATA[<p>It's just a few weeks into the hellscape that is a post-Roe United States... Sam and Mark chat about just a few of the stories that have come out in recent weeks illustrating the growing catastrophe. Donate to support the Indiana doctor currently under fire from fascist forces for providing abortion care to a 10 year old rape victim who traveled from Ohio <a href="https://www.gofundme.com/f/obgyns-supporting-dr-caitlin-bernard">here</a>.</p>
