<p><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2022/07/15/opinion/doctors-roe-v-wade-ohio-10-year-old.html">Dr. Caitlin Bernard Was Meant to Write This With Me Before She Was Attacked for Doing Her Job</a> by Tracey A. Wilkinson</p>
<p>Plus: some of the latest revelations on Trump's fascist coup attempt, which stretched far before the Jan 6th attack on the Capitol, see a few of our previous episodes to look deeper into the lead up:</p>
<p><a href="https://anchor.fm/refuse-fascism/episodes/Eric-Boehlert-Trump-plots-martial-law-from-White-House--the-press-shrugs-eogpus">#36 Eric Boehlert: Trump plots martial law from White House — the press shrugs</a> (Jan 3, 2021)</p>
