			<title><![CDATA[Overturning Roe: A Watershed Moment for U.S. Fascism]]></title>
			<description><![CDATA[<p>Sam and Coco Das discuss Coco's new article for The Independent: <a href="https://www.independent.co.uk/voices/roe-overturned-what-now-b2108765.html">Roe has been overturned and women’s bodies are no longer their own in America. Here’s what to do now</a>. Follow Coco at <a href="https://twitter.com/coco_das">@Coco_Das</a>.</p>
