			<description><![CDATA[<p>On our first post-Roe episode, we share some of the voices from the streets over the last couple days outside the Supreme Court demanding the federal government restore the fundamental right to abortion across the country NOW, including Sunsara Taylor (<a href="https://twitter.com/sunsarataylor">@sunsarataylor</a>), Paxton Smith (<a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@paxtonsmith?lang=en">@paxtonsmith</a>) and youth organizers.</p>
