			<title><![CDATA[Sunsara Taylor: Forced Motherhood = Female Enslavement]]></title>
			<description><![CDATA[<p>Sam Goldman shares thoughts and commentary on the latest fascist developments domestic and international. Then we share Sunsara Taylor's remarks from an event Feb. 16 at Revolution Books in Harlem on the abortion rights emergency in the US and a powerful call to action now - before Roe is overturned.&nbsp;</p>
