			<title><![CDATA[Town Hall on Abortion Rights Emergency]]></title>
			<description><![CDATA[<p>The extreme Texas Abortion Ban caught most people by surprise. Next &nbsp;month, the Supreme Court is scheduled to hear a direct challenge to the &nbsp;1973 landmark Roe v. Wade decision that legalized abortion. This round &nbsp;table aims to sound the alarm on this assault on women’s fundamental &nbsp;rights, deepen understanding of the stakes, arouse people’s fighting &nbsp;spirit to not let this go down, and explore what kind of future is &nbsp;possible and worth fighting for.</p>
<p>Hosted by Sunsara Taylor, writer for&nbsp;<a href="http://revcom.us/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">revcom.us</a>, host and producer of We Only Want the World on WBAI and WPFW, and co-host of The RNL — Revolution, Nothing Less — Show.</p>
