<p>A legal break-down by Dahlia Lithwick, who writes about the courts and the law for Slate and hosts the podcast Amicus.</p>
<p>A message from courageous abortion provider, Dr. Warren Hern.</p>
<p>A round-table between:</p>
<ul>
 <li>Sam Goldman, of the RefuseFascism.org Editorial Board and host of the Refuse Fascism Podcast</li>
