			<title><![CDATA[Caroline Duble: Texas's War on Abortion]]></title>
			<description><![CDATA[<p>Sam Goldman talks to Caroline Duble, the Political Director of Avow Texas (https://avowtexas.org/) about the abortion ban set to go into effect September 1st and the larger fight for abortion rights. Avow Texas' slogan is "Unapologetic Abortion Advocacy" (cheers for that!).</p>
