			<title><![CDATA[The Senate Impeachment Trial & the Need to Refuse Fascism]]></title>
			<description><![CDATA[<p>This urgent discussion was recorded February 8, on the eve of Trump’s &nbsp;second impeachment trial. What actually happened on January 6 when a &nbsp;fascist mob stormed the Capitol? What does that, and everything that &nbsp;lead up to it, tell us about the danger of fascism in America? How does the impeachment trial fit into this picture? And how can people act act &nbsp;in a meaningful way in the interests of humanity at this unprecedented &nbsp;moment?&nbsp;</p>
